        <item>
            <title>Apple 就 iPad Pro M4 版广告道歉    「广告未有达到预期目标」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/10/ipad-pro-crush/notebook/tablet-notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ipad-pro-crush</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/10/ipad-pro-crush/notebook/tablet-notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 08:00:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[平板电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPad Pro]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1234793</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>iPad Pro 平板电脑的广告出街后，被舆论严厉批评，指 Apple 粉碎人类创造力和文化成就的象征。Apple 副总裁 Tor Myhren 已就事件道歉，指「广告未有达到预期目标」。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Meet the new iPad Pro: the thinnest product we’ve ever created, the most advanced display we’ve ever produced, with the incredible power of the M4 chip. Just imagine all the things it’ll be used to create. <a href="https://t.co/6PeGXNoKgG">pic.twitter.com/6PeGXNoKgG</a></p><p>&mdash; Tim Cook (@tim_cook) <a href="https://twitter.com/tim_cook/status/1787864325258162239?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">May 7, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p style="text-align: center;">▲Apple 总裁 Tim Cook 在 X 上发布 iPad Pro 广告</p><p>Apple 在两日前发表新 iPad Pro，并推出名为「Crush!」广告，以工业印刷机为重点，压碎了大不少产品，例如小号、钢琴、相机、油漆罐和游戏机等，同时播放 Sonny &amp; Cher 的《All I Ever Need Is You》。Apple 总裁 Tim Cook 在 X 上发布影片，以「想像一下它将用来创造的所有东西」作贴文内容。</p><p>苹果行销副总裁 Tor Myhren 就广告道歉：「苹果向来赞美用户用各种方式表达自己，并透过 iPad 将他们的想法变为现实。我们的这段影片没有达到预期目标，对此我们深表歉意。」</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/business/business-news/apple-crushed-ipad-ad-backfires-company-apologizes-rcna151559">NBC</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/09/new-ipad-pro-2/notebook/tablet-notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">新 iPad Pro 被指基础版只有 3 高效核心，要 1TB/2TB 版本才有 4 高效核心</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/09/ipad-pro-2024-m4-review/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPad Pro 2024 M4 现场实试影片 : 解开变薄原因</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/08/ipad-pro-2024-first-impression/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【实试】iPad Pro / iPad Air 2024 上海实试，近距离试新荧幕 + 体验新 Apple Pencil Pro、新键盘</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/10/ipad-pro-crush/notebook/tablet-notebook/">Apple 就 iPad Pro M4 版广告道歉    「广告未有达到预期目标」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
